OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with cloud spreading
OL,7,Finland across the east. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will be dry and cloudy
OL,9,Fbut remaining clear across Dumfries
OL,10,Fand Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FDry. Rather cloudy
OL,13,Finitially in east, but sunshine across
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway spreading to
OL,15,Fmost late morning, but perhaps lower
OL,16,Fcloud lingering along east coast. Warm
OL,17,Fin southwest, cooler elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
